<text>LASD is the official abbreviation of the Los Angeles County Sheriff&#x27;s Department, a US local law enforcement agency.

LASD may also refer to:

*Leechburg Area School District
*Lehighton Area School District
*Littlestown Area School District
*Lockheed Aeronautics Services Division, a part of Lockheed Corporation
*Los Altos School District
*Lufthansa Airport Services Dresden GmbH
*FK Dinamo-Rīnuži/LASD, a football club in Riga, Latvia</text><links>
